      "description": "Five-loop equal-mass banana integral in D=2-2eps dimensions. Related to a Calabi-Yau 4-fold. First new result of this paper beyond the state of the art. Six master integrals M_0,...,M_5. The eps-expansion of M_1 starts at order eps^5: M_1^{(5,5)} = 288*zeta_5 + 480*zeta_3*I(1,Y_2) + I(1,Y_2,Y_2,1,f_{6,0}). Singular points at x in {4,16,36}. The special local normal form is theta_q^2 (1/Y_2) theta_q (1/Y_2) theta_q^2. Compared against pySecDec numerics with excellent agreement.",
